    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "From what I can see here, the rangeSlider values are based on the secondary query `facetStats`. The primary query does return results that are more in-line... ~~That seems to be a bug in the helper. I will have a look.~~ It's the expected behavior in the helper in order to get the outer bounds (without filters) however the engine seems to return wrong values (I'm asking some for some help from the engine team)",
